如果你没疯 那你就转给我看
If you're not crazy,
you can do that thing with your eyes.

162
00:20:20,123 --> 00:20:21,702
你没疯
You're not crazy.

163
00:20:21,843 --> 00:20:23,872
真好吃
This is delicious.

164
00:20:24,002 --> 00:20:25,911
你厨艺不错
You're a great cook.

165
00:20:26,051 --> 00:20:28,290
