- You don't have to prove yourself to them.

265
00:29:44,995 --> 00:29:47,524
你说的轻巧
当然 我亲眼所见
- That's easy for you to say.
- Of course I saw it.

266
00:29:47,664 --> 00:29:51,352
那个人顺着马路跑
这是浪漫和伤感的
- The man was running down the street.
- It's romantic, sentimental,

267
00:29:51,503 --> 00:29:54,451
他趴在我的车上
后工业化的胡扯
