- What seems to be the trouble?

270
00:30:00,710 --> 00:30:01,899
在吗？是的
Hello? Yeah.

271
00:30:02,049 --> 00:30:04,208
别把名字告诉警察
Don't ever give your name to cops.

272
00:30:04,339 --> 00:30:06,818
莱文沃思街跟塔克街路口 我等着
Leavenworth and Turk. I'll hold.

273
00:30:06,968 --> 00:30:09,127
但是他不是我的丈夫了
But he isn't my husband!

274
00:30:09,257 --> 00:30:11,876
他只是看着像而已 他是冒充的！
It's someone who looks like him.He's an impostor!

275
00:30:12,016 --> 00:30:15,784
好了 凯瑟琳 他就是你丈夫 你我都认识他
Now, Katherine, he's your husband.You know him and I know him.

276
00:30:15,935 --> 00:30:20,673
直到今天我才发现 因为他脖子后有一道疤
I had to wait until today cos he has a scar on the back of his neck

277
00:30:20,813 --> 00:30:23,292
他头发长的时候看不见
and when his hair is long you can't see it.

278
00:30:23,442 --> 00:30:26,890
他今天去理发…
疤不在了
- He went to have a haircut today...
- And the scar was gone.

279
00:30:27,771 --> 00:30:29,930
不 疤还在！
No! It's still there!

280
00:30:30,070 --> 00:30:33,558
当然还在那了 你说呢？他还是泰德
Of course it's still there.
What did you expect? He's still Ted.

281
00:30:33,698 --> 00:30:37,896
抱歉 我能说句话吗？
别这样！他仍然是你丈夫
- Excuse me, can I say one thing?
- Please! He's still your husband Ted.

282
00:30:38,027 --> 00:30:40,016
我知道一些事…
凯瑟琳？
- I know something...
- Katherine?

283
00:30:40,156 --> 00:30:41,975
我能说句话吗？
凯瑟琳？
- Could I say one thing?
- Katherine!

284
00:30:42,116 --> 00:30:43,485
稍等
Just a minute.

285
00:30:43,615 --> 00:30:45,944
凯瑟琳
给我一分钟就好 行吗？
- Katherine.
- Just give me a minute, will you?

286
00:30:46,074 --> 00:30:48,233
你相信我吗？
Will you trust me?

287
00:30:48,373 --> 00:30:51,531
相信我好吗？行吗？
Will you please trust me? Will you?

288
00:30:51,662 --> 00:30:54,900
我是公务员 这是一种爱国的表现
I work for the county.This is a public-spirited gesture.

289
00:30:55,041 --> 00:30:58,529
我会告诉你我的名字……
金博纳想让人适应世界
