296
00:31:16,264 --> 00:31:18,133
别这样
Come on.

297
00:31:18,263 --> 00:31:22,091
那里 这样挺好的 不是吗？我后面是谁？
There. That's not so bad, is it?Who's this behind me?

298
00:31:22,222 --> 00:31:24,591
是泰德
这就对了
- It's Ted.
- That's right.

299
00:31:24,731 --> 00:31:26,680
坚强点 就这样 坚强点
Hold on. Come on, just hold on.

300
00:31:26,810 --> 00:31:30,668
坚强点 放松点吧
Hold on. Just relax now.

301
00:31:30,819 --> 00:31:33,727
你会没事的 感觉好些了吗？
是的 是的
- You gonna be all right? You feel better?
- Yeah. Yes.

302
00:31:33,858 --> 00:31:35,807
你现在想回家了吗？
是的
- You wanna go home now?
- Yes.

303
00:31:35,947 --> 00:31:38,895
你们明天能来找我聊聊吗？
拜托了… 明天
- Will you come and see me tomorrow?
- Please... tomorrow.

304
00:31:39,026 --> 00:31:41,695
我们把话说透 好吗 我们三个？
Tomorrow we'll all talk. OK? The three of us?

305
00:31:41,825 --> 00:31:43,854
好的 但是我现在最好送她回家了
OK, but I better take her home.

306
00:31:43,994 --> 00:31:46,023
当然 没问题
Yes. It's OK.

307
00:31:46,153 --> 00:31:48,192
明天见
好的
- I'll see you tomorrow.
- OK.

308
00:31:48,663 --> 00:31:50,692
好吗？
好的
- All right?
- OK.

309
00:31:56,410 --> 00:31:57,819
谢谢
Thank you.

310
00:31:57,959 --> 00:32:00,278
他们对事故不感兴趣
They don't wanna hear about the accident.

311
00:32:00,419 --> 00:32:02,238
这是个大阴谋
It's a big conspiracy.

312
00:32:02,378 --> 00:32:04,577
什么是阴谋？
所有事
